eckoutservice**: The checkout service itself seems to have delays, potentially indicating internal processing issues or resource constraints.\n\n### JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"checkoutservice->checkoutservice\", \"cartservice->redis\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Average anomaly duration of GetCart operations exceeded normal duration significantly in multiple traces.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Significant increase in duration for multiple operations such as PaymentService/Charge indicating potential bottlenecks.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Substantial increase in processing time for HGET and HMSET commands indicating possible database latency.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThis analysis provides a starting point for root cause analysis by highlighting key performance bottlenecks observed in the trace data.", "metric_analysis_findings": "以下是故障期间显著的异常指标分析结果：\n\n### Detected Anomalies\n根据提供的异常指标数据，检测到以下指标变化：\n\n- **Node级别异常**\n  - `node_memory_usage_rate` 中 `aiops-k8s-04` 和 `aiops-k8s-05` 分别增加了 60.22% 和 52.29%。\n  - `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 中 `aiops-k8s-04` 和 `aiops-k8s-05` 分别减少了约 485% 和 33%。\n\n- **Pod级别指标**\n  - `redis-cart-0` 的 `pod_cpu_usage` 未显示显著异常，但常规故障分析中须重点关注。\n  \n- **Service级别指标**\n  - `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 在多个服务中，特别是 `cartservice` 和 `productcatalogservice` 有明显上升。\n  - `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 在 `shippingservice` 和 `cartservice` 有显著增幅，尤其是响应时间延迟增加。\n\n### Hypotheses\n1. **Node 自身异常**\n   - **Component**: `aiops-k8s-04` 和 `aiops-k8s-05`\n   - **Reason**: `node_memory_usage_rate` 和 `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 显著变化表明节点可能受到资源瓶颈或系统进程问题。\n   - **Evidence**: `node_memory_usage_rate` 上升超过50%，以及可